{"tid":797693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件畢業營趣事","createTime":"2018-08-28T16:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T05:28:58.000Z","uid":153267,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8cdad6b4bfb887856f8f3e129ed83fe7dfd671","tid":797693,"uid":153267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T16:46:52.000Z","msg":"話說當年我既年代就仲未興用手機睇AV嘅<br />\n而我間學校既小學雞就好撚古惑咸濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚成班男仔係間房到唔知做乜鳩好 大家又正值青春旺盛嘅時期 就用左手機打咸濕電話聽 好似打通左就會有條女係到呻吟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當我地成班十鳩幾個男仔開住個擴音圍埋聽得興起之際 我地既女班主任巡房入撚左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 跟住比佢見到我地成班男仔 圍哂係中間播住淫叫聲 真係嚇到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後佢嬲到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班男仔比阿sir 的左出去掃樹葉 掃撚左成個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f0a622ffe1ef5c227e994e4afc8158be561986","tid":797693,"uid":153267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post 冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae9859575a561ca8bb49fb2923f875df5dadf57","tid":797693,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"我個陣頂多係成班男仔半夜比人的出房罰做掌上壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e2c6a5b01aa35927cd02d225626d012a38f558","tid":797693,"uid":153267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bae9859575a561ca8bb49fb2923f875df5dadf57","tid":797693,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"我個陣頂多係成班男仔半夜比人的出房罰做掌上壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20